Q: Implement an algorithm for making a simple calculator with all the operators (+,-,*,/,%)

Ask the user to enter Num1.
Ask the user to enter Num2.
Ask the user to enter the operator(+,-,*,/,%).
If the operator is "+" then
    Set Ans=Num1+Num2
    Display the value of "Ans".
Else if the operator is "-" then
    Set Ans=Num1-Num2
    Display the value of "Ans".
Else if the operator is "*" then
    Set Ans=Num1*Num2
    Display the value of "Ans".
Else if the operator is "/" then
     If Num2 is not 0
         Set Ans=Num1/Num2
         Display the value of "Ans".
     Else
         Display "Cannot divided by zero" 
Else if the operator is "%" then
     Set Ans=Num1%Num2
     Display the value of "Ans".
Else
     Display "Invalid operator".

